public final class PrecedenceVDisjoint
extends AbstractPrecedenceSConstraint

if b is true then t1 ends before t2, otherwise t2 ends before t1. same as PrecedenceDisjoint when at least one tasks has a variable duration. b = 1 <=> e1 <= s2 b = 0 <=> e2 <= s1
